layNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":71,"left":null,"right":71},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":72,"text":"+This is the **only** section where AI usage is expected and encouraged.","html":"+This is the \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eonly\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e section where AI usage is expected and encouraged.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":72,"left":null,"right":72},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":73,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":73,"left":null,"right":73},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":74,"text":"+- Replace the \"Something Missing? Generate a relevant section with AI\" placeholder with a brand-new section of your own idea.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Replace the \u0026quot;Something Missing? Generate a relevant section with AI\u0026quot; placeholder with a brand-new section of your own idea.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":74,"left":null,"right":74},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":75,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":75,"left":null,"right":75},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":76,"text":"+- The section **must stay relevant to the DevConf 2026 theme** (e.g. Sponsors, Countdown Timer, Venue/Location Map, FAQ, Newsletter Signup, Hackathon Details, Past Highlights, Job Board, etc.).","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e The section \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003emust stay relevant to the DevConf 2026 theme\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e (e.g. Sponsors, Countdown Timer, Venue/Location Map, FAQ, Newsletter Signup, Hackathon Details, Past Highlights, Job Board, etc.).","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":76,"left":null,"right":76},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":77,"text":"+- Use AI (Claude, ChatGPT, or any tool) to help you **ideate, design, and/or code** this section.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u00