osition":84,"left":null,"right":84},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":85,"text":"+- You must **submit the prompt(s)** you used to generate this section along with your submission (see Submission Format below).","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e You must \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003esubmit the prompt(s)\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e you used to generate this section along with your submission (see Submission Format below).","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":85,"left":null,"right":85},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":86,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":86,"left":null,"right":86},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":87,"text":"+---","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-ms\"\u003e---\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":87,"left":null,"right":87},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":88,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":88,"left":null,"right":88},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":89,"text":"+## 🔸 Other Requirements (Must Follow)","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-mh\"\u003e## \u003cspan class=\"pl-en\"\u003e🔸 Other Requirements (Must Follow)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":89,"left":null,"right":89},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":90,"text":"+- Minimum **5 GitHub commits**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Minimum \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e5 GitHub commits\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":90,"left":null,"right":90},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":91,"text":"+- **No Lorem Ipsum** text anywhere on the website","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eNo Lorem Ipsum\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e text anywhere on the website","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":91,"left":null,"right":91},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":92,"text":"+- No duplicated/copy-pasted text across repeating sections (e.g. each speaker bio/description must be unique)","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e No duplicated/copy-pasted text across repeating sections (e.g. each speaker bio/description must be unique)","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":92,"left":null,"right":92},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":93,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":93,"left":null,"right":93},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":94,"text":"+---","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-ms\"\u003e---\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":94,"left":null,"right":94},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":95,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":95,"left":null,"right":95},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":96,"text":"+## 🎥 ADDITIONAL REQUIREMENT — Concept Explanation Video (Optional, 0 Marks)","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-mh\"\u003e## \u003cspan class=\"pl-en\"\u003e🎥 ADDITIONAL REQUIREMENT — Concept Explanation Video (Optional, 0 Marks)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":96,"left":null,"right":96},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":97,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":97,"left":null,"right":97},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":98,"text":"+\u003e ⚠️ **This is fully optional and carries no marks in this assignment. However, it is highly recommended.** Starting from the next assignment, submitting a short explanation video like this will become **mandatory**, so use this one to get comfortable with the format early.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-ent\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-ent\"\u003e\u0026gt; \u003c/span\u003e⚠️ \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eThis is fully optional and carries no marks in this assignment. However, it is highly recommended.\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e Starting from the next assignment, submitting a short explanation video like this will become \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003emandatory\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e, so use this one to get comfortable with the format early.\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":98,"left":null,"right":98},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":99,"text":"+","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-ent\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":99,"left":null,"right":99},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":100,"text":"+- Record a **max 5-minute video** explaining the following basic HTML \u0026 CSS questions in your own words:","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Record a \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003emax 5-minute video\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e explaining the following basic HTML \u0026amp; CSS questions in your own words:","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":100,"left":null,"right":100},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":101,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":101,"left":null,"right":101},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":102,"text":"+  1. What is the difference between a `\u003cdiv\u003e` and a `\u003cspan\u003e`? When would you use each?","html":"+  \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e What is the difference between a \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003e\u0026lt;div\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e and a \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003e\u0026lt;span\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e? When would you use each?","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":102,"left":null,"right":102},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":103,"text":"+  2. What is the CSS Box Model? Explain `content`, `padding`, `border`, and `margin`.","html":"+  \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e What is the CSS Box Model? Explain \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003econtent\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003epadding\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003eborder\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e, and \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003emargin\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":103,"left":null,"right":103},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":104,"text":"+  3. What is the difference between a CSS `class` and an `id`? When should you use one over the other?","html":"+  \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e What is the difference between a CSS \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003eclass\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e and an \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003eid\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e? When should you use one over the other?","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":104,"left":null,"right":104},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":105,"text":"+  4. What is Flexbox, and what's the difference between `justify-content` and `align-items`?","html":"+  \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e What is Flexbox, and what\u0026#39;s the difference between \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003ejustify-content\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e and \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003ealign-items\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e?","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":105,"left":null,"right":105},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":106,"text":"+  5. What is the difference between `position: relative`, `absolute`, and `fixed` in CSS?","html":"+  \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e5\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e What is the difference between \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003eposition: relative\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003eabsolute\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e, and \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003efixed\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e in CSS?","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":106,"left":null,"right":106},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":107,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":107,"left":null,"right":107},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":108,"text":"+- Speak naturally, in your own words — no need to read from a script.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Speak naturally, in your own words — no need to read from a script.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":108,"left":null,"right":108},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":109,"text":"+- Screen recording with your face on camera (or voice-over on slides/code) is fine, whichever you're comfortable with.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Screen recording with your face on camera (or voice-over on slides/code) is fine, whichever you\u0026#39;re comfortable with.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":109,"left":null,"right":109},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":110,"text":"+- Upload the video link (YouTube/Google Drive) along with your submission.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Upload the video link (YouTube/Google Drive) along with your submission.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":110,"left":null,"right":110},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":111,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":111,"left":null,"right":111},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":112,"text":"+---","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-ms\"\u003e---\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":112,"left":null,"right":112},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":113,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":113,"left":null,"right":113},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":114,"text":"+## 🛠️ Tech Stack","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-mh\"\u003e## \u003cspan class=\"pl-en\"\u003e🛠️ Tech Stack\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":114,"left":null,"right":114},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":115,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":115,"left":null,"right":115},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":116,"text":"+- HTML5","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e HTML5","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":116,"left":null,"right":116},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":117,"text":"+- CSS3","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e CSS3","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":117,"left":null,"right":117},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":118,"text":"+- No JavaScript","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e No JavaScript","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":118,"left":null,"right":118},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":119,"text":"+- No CSS frameworks or libraries","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e No CSS frameworks or libraries","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":119,"left":null,"right":119},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":120,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":120,"left":null,"right":120},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":121,"text":"+---","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-ms\"\u003e---\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":121,"left":null,"right":121},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":122,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":122,"left":null,"right":122},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":123,"text":"+## 📂 Submission Format","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-mh\"\u003e## \u003cspan class=\"pl-en\"\u003e📂 Submission Format\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":123,"left":null,"right":123},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":124,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":124,"left":null,"right":124},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":125,"text":"+- **GitHub Repository Link**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eGitHub Repository Link\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":125,"left":null,"right":125},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":126,"text":"+- **Live Website Link (GitHub Pages)**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eLive Website Link (GitHub Pages)\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":126,"left":null,"right":126},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":127,"text":"+- **AI Prompt(s)** used for the Placeholder Section (paste as text, or include in a `PROMPTS.md` file in your repo)","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eAI Prompt(s)\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e used for the Placeholder Section (paste as text, or include in a \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003ePROMPTS.md\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e file in your repo)","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":127,"left":null,"right":127},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":128,"text":"+- **(Optional) Concept Explanation Video Link**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e(Optional) Concept Explanation Video Link\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":128,"left":null,"right":128},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":129,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":129,"left":null,"right":129},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":130,"text":"+---","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-ms\"\u003e---\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":130,"left":null,"right":130},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":131,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":131,"left":null,"right":131},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":132,"text":"+## ❓ Common Questions \u0026 Answers","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-mh\"\u003e## \u003cspan class=\"pl-en\"\u003e❓ Common Questions \u0026amp; Answers\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":132,"left":null,"right":132},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":133,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":133,"left":null,"right":133},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":134,"text":"+**Can I use different images?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eCan I use different images?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":134,"left":null,"right":134},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":135,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":135,"left":null,"right":135},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":136,"text":"+- Yes, you may use any relevant images (speaker photos, hero background, etc.).","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Yes, you may use any relevant images (speaker photos, hero background, etc.).","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":136,"left":null,"right":136},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":137,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":137,"left":null,"right":137},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":138,"text":"+**Can I change the alignment and design freely?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eCan I change the alignment and design freely?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":138,"left":null,"right":138},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":139,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":139,"left":null,"right":139},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":140,"text":"+- No. You must follow the alignment and layout shown in the Figma design.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e No. You must follow the alignment and layout shown in the Figma design.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":140,"left":null,"right":140},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":141,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":141,"left":null,"right":141},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":142,"text":"+**Can I change colors?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eCan I change colors?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":142,"left":null,"right":142},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":143,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":143,"left":null,"right":143},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":144,"text":"+- Yes, as long as the colors are relevant and visually consistent with a tech-conference theme.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Yes, as long as the colors are relevant and visually consistent with a tech-conference theme.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":144,"left":null,"right":144},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":145,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":145,"left":null,"right":145},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":146,"text":"+**Do I need to make the page pixel-perfect?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eDo I need to make the page pixel-perfect?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":146,"left":null,"right":146},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":147,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":147,"left":null,"right":147},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":148,"text":"+- No. You can use your own margin and padding while following the overall structure from Figma.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e No. You can use your own margin and padding while following the overall structure from Figma.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":148,"left":null,"right":148},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":149,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":149,"left":null,"right":149},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":150,"text":"+**Can I use AI to build my sections?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eCan I use AI to build my sections?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":150,"left":null,"right":150},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":151,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":151,"left":null,"right":151},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":152,"text":"+- Only for the **Placeholder Section** (see below). For every other section, you are expected to write the HTML \u0026 CSS yourself. Using AI to generate the Navbar, Banner, Speakers, Pricing, or Footer sections is **not recommended** and may cost marks during evaluation.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Only for the \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003ePlaceholder Section\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e (see below). For every other section, you are expected to write the HTML \u0026amp; CSS yourself. Using AI to generate the Navbar, Banner, Speakers, Pricing, or Footer sections is \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003enot recommended\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e and may cost marks during evaluation.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":152,"left":null,"right":152},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":153,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":153,"left":null,"right":153},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":154,"text":"+**Is the explanation video mandatory?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eIs the explanation video mandatory?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":154,"left":null,"right":154},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":155,"text":"+- No, not for this assignment. It's optional and won't be graded, but it's a good habit to build early since it will be mandatory starting next assignment.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e No, not for this assignment. It\u0026#39;s optional and won\u0026#39;t be graded, but it\u0026#39;s a good habit to build early since it will be mandatory starting next assignment.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":155,"left":null,"right":155},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":156,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":156,"left":null,"right":156},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":157,"text":"+---","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-ms\"\u003e---\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":157,"left":null,"right":157},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":158,"text":"+---","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-ms\"\u003e---\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":158,"left":null,"right":158},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":159,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":159,"left":null,"right":159},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":160,"text":"+## ❓ Common Issues You May Face and Quick Solutions","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-mh\"\u003e## \u003cspan class=\"pl-en\"\u003e❓ Common Issues You May Face and Quick Solutions\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":160,"left":null,"right":160},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":161,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":161,"left":null,"right":161},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":162,"text":"+**GitHub Pages showing 404 / site not loading?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eGitHub Pages showing 404 / site not loading?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":162,"left":null,"right":162},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":163,"text":"+- Your main HTML file **must be named `index.html`** (lowercase). GitHub Pages looks for this file by default. Rename it if it's called anything else (e.g. `home.html`, `Index.html`).","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Your main HTML file \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003emust be named \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003eindex.html\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e (lowercase). GitHub Pages looks for this file by default. Rename it if it\u0026#39;s called anything else (e.g. \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003ehome.html\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003eIndex.html\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e).","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":163,"left":null,"right":163},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":164,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":164,"left":null,"right":164},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":165,"text":"+**Images or CSS not loading on GitHub Pages?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eImages or CSS not loading on GitHub Pages?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":165,"left":null,"right":165},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":166,"text":"+- Add `./` before your file paths: `./style.css`, `./images/photo.jpg` instead of `style.css` or `/images/photo.jpg`.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Add \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003e./\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e before your file paths: \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003e./style.css\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003e./images/photo.jpg\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e instead of \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003estyle.css\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e or \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003e/images/photo.jpg\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":166,"left":null,"right":166},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":167,"text":"+- File names are **case-sensitive** on GitHub Pages (Linux). `Photo.jpg` ≠ `photo.jpg` — make sure casing matches exactly.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e File names are \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003ecase-sensitive\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e on GitHub Pages (Linux). \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003ePhoto.jpg\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e ≠ \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003ephoto.jpg\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e — make sure casing matches exactly.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":167,"left":null,"right":167},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":168,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":168,"left":null,"right":168},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":169,"text":"+**CSS background image not showing?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eCSS background image not showing?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":169,"left":null,"right":169},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":170,"text":"+- Paths in CSS `background-image: url(...)` are relative to the **CSS file location**, not the HTML file. Use `./images/bg.jpg` or `../images/bg.jpg` depending on your folder structure.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Paths in CSS \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003ebackground-image: url(...)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e are relative to the \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eCSS file location\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e, not the HTML file. Use \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003e./images/bg.jpg\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e or \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003e../images/bg.jpg\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e depending on your folder structure.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":170,"left":null,"right":170},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":171,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":171,"left":null,"right":171},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":172,"text":"+**Site not updating after pushing to GitHub?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eSite not updating after pushing to GitHub?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":172,"left":null,"right":172},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":173,"text":"+- Wait 1–2 minutes, then hard refresh: `Ctrl + Shift + R` (Windows) / `Cmd + Shift + R` (Mac) to bypass browser cache.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Wait 1–2 minutes, then hard refresh: \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003eCtrl + Shift + R\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e (Windows) / \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003eCmd + Shift + R\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e (Mac) to bypass browser cache.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":173,"left":null,"right":173},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":174,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":174,"left":null,"right":174},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":175,"text":"+**CSS changes not reflecting locally?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eCSS changes not reflecting locally?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":175,"left":null,"right":175},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":176,"text":"+- Hard refresh: `Ctrl + Shift + R`. Your browser is likely showing a cached version.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Hard refresh: \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003eCtrl + Shift + R\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e. Your browser is likely showing a cached version.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":176,"left":null,"right":176},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":177,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":177,"left":null,"right":177},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":178,"text":"+**Commit count is less than 5?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eCommit count is less than 5?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":178,"left":null,"right":178},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":179,"text":"+- Commit after completing each section (Navbar → Banner → Speakers → Pricing → Footer). Don't push everything in one final commit.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e Commit after completing each section (Navbar → Banner → Speakers → Pricing → Footer). Don\u0026#39;t push everything in one final commit.","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":179,"left":null,"right":179},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":180,"text":"+","html":"+","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":180,"left":null,"right":180},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":181,"text":"+**Fonts or icons not loading?**","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003eFonts or icons not loading?\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e**\u003c/span\u003e","displayNoNewLineWarning":false,"position":181,"left":null,"right":181},{"type":"ADDITION","blobLineNumber":182,"text":"+- If using Google Fonts or icon libraries via `\u003clink\u003e`, they require an internet connection. They will work fine on GitHub Pages.","html":"+\u003cspan class=\"pl-v\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e If using Google Fonts or icon libraries via \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-c1\"\u003e\u0026lt;link\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e`\u003c/span\u003e, they require an internet connection. They will work fine on GitHub Pages