le="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionLine-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-line)); padding-right: 24px;"><code class="diff-text syntax-highlighted-line addition"><span class="diff-text-marker">+</span><div class="diff-text-inner"><span class="pl-s">**</span>GitHub Pages showing 404 / site not loading?<span class="pl-s">**</span></div></code></td></tr><tr class="diff-line-row" data-row-selected="false"><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-163-0" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code></code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-163-1" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code>163</code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-163-2" data-line-anchor="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031R163" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-text-cell right-side-diff-cell  left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionLine-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-line)); padding-right: 24px;"><code class="diff-text syntax-highlighted-line addition"><span class="diff-text-marker">+</span><div class="diff-text-inner"><span class="pl-v">-</span> Your main HTML file <span class="pl-s">**</span>must be named <span class="pl-s">`</span><span class="pl-c1">index.html</span><span class="pl-s">`</span><span class="pl-s">**</span> (lowercase). GitHub Pages looks for this file by default. Rename it if it's called anything else (e.g. <span class="pl-s">`</span><span class="pl-c1">home.html</span><span class="pl-s">`</span>, <span class="pl-s">`</span><span class="pl-c1">Index.html</span><span class="pl-s">`</span>).</div></code></td></tr><tr class="diff-line-row" data-row-selected="false"><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-164-0" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code></code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-164-1" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code>164</code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-164-2" data-line-anchor="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031R164" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-text-cell right-side-diff-cell tmp-pt-4 left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionLine-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-line)); padding-right: 24px;"><code class="diff-text syntax-highlighted-line addition"><span class="diff-text-marker">+</span><div class="diff-text-inner"></div></code></td></tr><tr class="diff-line-row" data-row-selected="false"><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-165-0" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code></code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-165-1" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code>165</code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-165-2" data-line-anchor="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031R165" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-text-cell right-side-diff-cell  left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionLine-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-line)); padding-right: 24px;"><code class="diff-text syntax-highlighted-line addition"><span class="diff-text-marker">+</span><div class="diff-text-inner"><span class="pl-s">**</span>Images or CSS not loading on GitHub Pages?<span class="pl-s">**</span></div></code></td></tr><tr class="diff-line-row" data-row-selected="false"><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-166-0" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code></code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-166-1" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code>166</code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-166-2" data-line-anchor="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031R166" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-text-cell right-side-diff-cell  left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionLine-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-line)); padding-right: 24px;"><code class="diff-text syntax-highlighted-line addition"><span class="diff-text-marker">+</span><div class="diff-text-inner"><span class="pl-v">-</span> Add <span class="pl-s">`</span><span class="pl-c1">./</span><span class="pl-s">`</span> before your file paths: <span class="pl-s">`</span><span class="pl-c1">./style.css</span><span class="pl-s">`</span>, <span class="pl-s">`</span><span class="pl-c1">./images/photo.jpg</span><span class="pl-s">`</span> instead of <span class="pl-s">`</span><span class="pl-c1">style.css</span><span class="pl-s">`</span> or <span class="pl-s">`</span><span class="pl-c1">/images/photo.jpg</span><span class="pl-s">`</span>.</div></code></td></tr><tr class="diff-line-row" data-row-selected="false"><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-167-0" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code></code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-167-1" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code>167</code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-167-2" data-line-anchor="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031R167" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-text-cell right-side-diff-cell  left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionLine-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-line)); padding-right: 24px;"><code class="diff-text syntax-highlighted-line addition"><span class="diff-text-marker">+</span><div class="diff-text-inner"><span class="pl-v">-</span> File names are <span class="pl-s">**</span>case-sensitive<span class="pl-s">**</span> on GitHub Pages (Linux). <span class="pl-s">`</span><span class="pl-c1">Photo.jpg</span><span class="pl-s">`</span> ≠ <span class="pl-s">`</span><span class="pl-c1">photo.jpg</span><span class="pl-s">`</span> — make sure casing matches exactly.</div></code></td></tr><tr class="diff-line-row" data-row-selected="false"><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-168-0" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code></code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-168-1" data-selected="false" role="gridcell" tabindex="-1" valign="top" class="focusable-grid-cell diff-line-number position-relative left-side" style="background-color: var(--diffBlob-additionNum-bgColor, var(--diffBlob-addition-bgColor-num)); text-align: center;"><code>168</code></td><td data-grid-cell-id="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc28928dfef526912b5f52356ff43651369bae92f56031-empty-168-2" data-line-anchor="diff-1550ec65ac92f65817fc2